name: Bluebird of Happiness
description:
Archival quality original watercolor illustrations.

On acid free 9" x 12", 140lbs. Fabriano watercolor. Suitable for framing. It is signed and dated in the front.

All original watercolors will be shipped inside a stay flat envelope with a clear DO NOT BEND sign in the front.

Prints ship from Miami, FL. 

Thanks so much for visiting my shop!
